---
/**
 * About.astro - "Sobre mí" section for Gabriel's CV 2.0
 * PR3: Content Components
 */

---

<section id="about" class="about-section">
  <div class="about-container">
    <!-- Section Title -->
    <h2 class="section-title" data-reveal data-i18n="about.title">
      Sobre mí
      <span class="title-accent"></span>
    </h2>

    <div class="about-content">
      <!-- Left Column: Text -->
      <div class="about-text" data-reveal>
        <p data-i18n="about.text">
          Desarrollador Full Stack con experiencia en el desarrollo de aplicaciones web y móviles. Apasionado por construir soluciones escalables y el aprendizaje continuo. Mi background en educación y ciberseguridad aporta una perspectiva única en el desarrollo de software seguro y accesible.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text-secondary">
          <span data-i18n="about.secondary">Me esfuerzo por escribir código limpio, mantenible y orientado a soluciones que generan impacto real en los usuarios.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Stats -->
      <div class="about-stats" data-reveal>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number" data-i18n="about.years">7+</span>
          <span class="stat-label" data-i18n="about.years_label">Años programando</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number" data-i18n="about.projects">2+</span>
          <span class="stat-label" data-i18n="about.projects_label">Proyectos completados</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number" data-i18n="about.techs">15+</span>
          <span class="stat-label" data-i18n="about.techs_label">Tecnologías dominadas</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Personal Traits -->
    <div class="about-traits" data-reveal>
      <span class="trait-badge" data-i18n="about.trait_curious">Curioso</span>
      <span class="trait-badge" data-i18n="about.trait_organized">Organizado</span>
      <span class="trait-badge" data-i18n="about.trait_teamplayer">Trabajo en equipo</span>
      <span class="trait-badge" data-i18n="about.trait_learner">Aprendizaje continuo</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Section */
  .about-section {
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--bg-surface);
  }

  .about-container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Section Title */
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .title-accent {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -8px;
    left: 0;
    width: 60%;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--neon-cyan), var(--neon-blue));
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
  }

  /* Content Grid */
  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* Text Column */
  .about-text {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-text p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-text-secondary {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  /* Stats Column */
  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about-stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-default);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 1.25rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .stat-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-primary);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--accent-glow);
  }

  .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* Traits */
  .about-traits {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-traits {
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }
  }

  .trait-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-default);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .trait-badge:hover {
    border-color: var(--neon-cyan);
    color: var(--neon-cyan);
  }
</style>